'''Windows Holographic'''是一个[[增强现实|增强现实]]的计算平台，由[[微软|微软]]推出。它在[[Windows_10|Windows 10]]操作系统于2015年发布的时候被引入。<ref name="Forbes">{{cite web|last1=Kain|first1=Erik|title=Microsoft Augments Reality With Windows Holographic|url=http://www.forbes.com/sites/erikkain/2015/01/21/microsoft-augments-reality-with-windows-holographic/|website=Forbes|accessdate=21 January 2015|date=21 January 2015|archive-date=2015-01-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150121194227/http://www.forbes.com/sites/erikkain/2015/01/21/microsoft-augments-reality-with-windows-holographic/}}</ref><ref name="BW">{{cite web|last1=Myerson|first1=Terry|title=The next generation of Windows: Windows 10|url=http://blogs.windows.com/bloggingwindows/2015/01/21/the-next-generation-of-windows-windows-10/|website=Blogging Windows|publisher=Microsoft|accessdate=21 January 2015|date=21 January 2015|archive-date=2015-01-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150121193023/http://blogs.windows.com/bloggingwindows/2015/01/21/the-next-generation-of-windows-windows-10/|dead-url=no}}</ref>使用Windows Holographic的[[API|API]]可以使得所有版本的Windows 10（包括[[智能手机|智能手机]]和[[平板电脑|平板电脑]]上的版本）使用增强现实功能，并且可以容易地在任何Windows应用程式上实现。<ref name="livestream">{{cite AV media |people=Terry Myerson, Alex Kipman, Jeff Norris, Satya Nadella |date=21 January 2015 |title=Windows 10: The Next Chapter |medium= |url=https://ll.ms-studiosmedia.com/events/2015/1501/Windows10CP/live/Windows10CP.html |access-date=22 January 2015 |format= |time=01:36:53 |location= |publisher=Microsoft |archive-date=2015-04-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150412031218/https://ll.ms-studiosmedia.com/events/2015/1501/Windows10CP/live/Windows10CP.html |dead-url=yes }}</ref>微软在2015年1月21日的“Windows 10：下一篇章”新闻发布会上发布了Windows Holographic。<ref name="Verge">{{cite web |last=Shaban |first=Hamza |url=http://www.theverge.com/2015/1/21/7867593/microsoft-announces-windows-holographic |title=Microsoft announces Windows Holographic with HoloLens headset |publisher=The Verge |date=2014-09-02 |accessdate=2015-01-21 |archive-date=2015-01-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150122011759/http://www.theverge.com/2015/1/21/7867593/microsoft-announces-windows-holographic |dead-url=no }}</ref>

